Privacy Policy for Secure Password Generator
This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which Secure Password Generator (the "App") collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users (each, a "User") of the App.

1. No Personal Information Is Collected

Secure Password Generator is designed to work completely offline and on your device only. We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal information from our users. All password generation logic and data processing occurs directly on your device.

2. No Internet Access or Data Transmission

The App does not require an internet connection to function. It does not connect to any servers or third-party services to transmit or receive data. Your generated passwords and settings remain entirely on your device.

3. No Third-Party Services

The App does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or other services that could collect your personal information.

4. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. When we do, we will update the date at the bottom of this page. We encourage Users to check this page periodically for any changes to stay informed about how we are protecting the personal information we don't collect. You acknowledge and agree that it is your responsibility to review this Privacy Policy periodically and become aware of modifications.

5. Your Acceptance of These Terms

By using this App, you signify your acceptance of this policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please do not use our App. Your continued use of the App following the posting of changes to this policy will be deemed your acceptance of those changes.

